<hgroup><h1>A practical algorithm for finding maximal exact matches in large sequence datasets using sparse suffix arrays</h1></hgroup><div class="cg p">
<a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term=%22Khan%20Z%22%5BAuthor%5D" class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id1"><span class="name western">Zia Khan</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id1">
